        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">3 Mistakes That Kill Shopify App YouTube Channels</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Publishing Product Updates Instead of Search Content</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Release notes and feature announcement videos reach only the merchants who already installed. Nobody searches "version 2.4 changelog". Every production slot spent on update content is a slot not spent on the roundup or comparison query that brings in new installs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Measuring Views Instead of Installs</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">A video with 400 views from a "best apps" query can drive more installs than one with 40,000 views from a trending topic. Judge the channel on view counts and you will optimize toward exactly the content that never converts. Judge it on listing traffic and installs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
