          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Quitting Before the Compounding Starts</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Search-driven video takes months to rank, then keeps converting for years. The 12-month experiment above grew every single month, and month 12 looked nothing like month 3. Channels abandoned in the first quarter walk away right before the curve bends.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Production Actually Takes -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-2">The Effort Question</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">What Producing 4 Videos a Month Actually Takes</h2>
